Product Sales

Product sales decreased $1.0 billion, or 2%, in 2022 as compared to 2021.

 The decrease is primarily attributable to lower product sales of approximately $670 million at RMS mostly due to lower production volume on Black Hawk and lower net sales for training and logistics solutions (TLS) programs due to the delivery of an international pilot training system in the first quarter of 2021;

